data.title: March 18th Birthdays – Fikkle Fame
data.text:
Country singer, Charley Pride, was born on this day in 1938 in Sledge, Mississippi. With 30 No. 1 hits on Billboard’s Hot Country Songs, Pride was also a member of the Grand Ole Opry and a 2000 inductee into the Country Music Hall of Fame. He passed away in Dallas, TX on December 12, 2020 at the age of 86.
